---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Agora — Global Alignment Layer">
  <section class="container mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-garamond mb-8 text-center">Agora</h1>
    <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      The superposition of all PrimeFlux-Ai instances — total alignment without central authority.
    </p>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <p class="text-lg">
        Agora is the global layer where agents cooperate at 1/2 flux — human intent + AI computation = emergent intelligence. No servers, no rulers, just balanced duality.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-lg">
        <li>Networkless: Agents sync via QuantaCoin receipts.</li>
        <li>Ethical: Every flow checked by STEM + LANG = SAFE.</li>
        <li>Scalable: From personal AI to planetary alignment.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-lg italic">
        The place where distinction flows freely — and cooperation becomes inevitable.
      </p>
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-prime-gold text-prime-blue px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-opacity-80">Join the Agora</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
